attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: South End-style parlor triplex set in a 2-unit brick rowhouse overlooking the Boston and Seaport skyline. Comprising nearly 1,800 sqft, this 2016 construction condo blends traditional and modern stylings and offers 3 beds + office and 3.5 baths plus generous outdoor living. Parlor living/dining room features 10' ceilings, gas FP, and a wall of glass sliders opening onto a spacious deck with views, complete with piped gas grill. Incredible kitchen w/Thermador appliances, waterfall center island + separate wet bar and wine fridge. King-sized owner's bedroom has city views and an ensuite bath & walk-in closet while the two spacious guest bedrooms each offer a private bath. A separate office allows for a work-from-home area or possible 4th bed. Completing this home is a sizable private terrace, connected to the upper deck via spiral stairs, providing an ideal entertaining space. Add'l features include in-ceiling speakers, central AC, and 1 direct-access rental parking, prepaid for 1 year.
